{"tid":1466421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家應該冷靜啲","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:08.000Z","uid":7334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37e425fe9a426652bbeb95ff2146b9e2a91d967d","tid":1466421,"uid":7334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"懷疑偽冒記者單野<br />\n如果我係普通市民睇新聞會覺得似係批鬥中國人<br />\n<br />\n我地一直都係贏民心<br />\n呢一點毋庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n話就話放核彈都唔割席<br />\n但大家打還打但都要冷靜分輕重<br />\n第一，唔好打死人，睇住唔好打要害<br />\n第二，配合FA，如FA 覺得你地打夠，再打就出事就應該出手阻止，勇武都唔應該繼續打<br />\n第三， 唔好阻人上白車，呢啲係黑警行為<br />\n<br />\n理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271c4e4cb5565ae490243ebb00150325b597fae3","tid":1466421,"uid":7334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"83c7b46a05677bdb1d7b6350545f85ce7550c153","tid":1466421,"uid":7334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"打交要食腦"},{"pid":"cb1f8f8b3d787c6e2c82276befabea0714433782","tid":1466421,"uid":7334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"利申： 呢個係學術研討"},{"pid":"3a38b5d017d856e0ce2510c434c5b2bde7eb7690","tid":1466421,"uid":7334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec842dd8aecfa2891961119a0103a2cc11d6edaf","tid":1466421,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a4952d63f449a395221e8d6abec2307ae598448","tid":1466421,"uid":7334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"真係要冷靜"},{"pid":"ec712366bb6f00b0e2541d36eb393dce152b53d6","tid":1466421,"uid":264793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"係咪真係要打呢？發洩方法有好多種，只要做到同樣效果，其實真係未必做到打人依步。打人除時打死人，影響民意，同埋除時打到自己人，頭先都打到一位自己兄弟。<br />\n<br />\n建議下次搵到鬼，除撚哂佢啲衫，綁佢係條柱到視眾，仲要唔比佢坐。"},{"pid":"ef9